des:
BN-LINK Smart products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your outlets.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your outlets - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your outlets products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "BN-LINK Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "BN-LINK Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some BN-LINK Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "BN-LINK Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "BN-LINK Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "BN-LINK Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "BN-LINK Smart", and you'll be navigated to "BN-LINK Smart" login page;
(9). Open “BN-LINK Smart“ App, click More Service, choose “Alexa”. Link with Verification Code, copy the Code, put code into the login page；
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the outlet.”
“Alexa, turn off the outlet.”
